org.sql: SELECT journals.id AS event_id, journals.created_at AS event_datetime, journals.user_id AS event_author, journals.notes AS event_description, journals.version AS version, journals.journable_id AS journable_id, message_journals.subject AS message_subject, message_journals.content AS message_content, message_journals.parent_id AS message_parent_id, forums.id AS forum_id, forums.name AS forum_name, forums.project_id AS project_id FROM journals INNER JOIN message_journals ON journals.data_id = message_journals.id AND journals.data_type = 'Journal::MessageJournal' INNER JOIN forums ON message_journals.forum_id = forums.id INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = forums.project_id WHERE journals.journable_type = 'Message' AND journals.user_id = 653 AND projects.id IN (SELECT enabled_modules.project_id FROM enabled_modules WHERE name = 'activity') AND projects.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT projects.id FROM projects INNER JOIN enabled_modules ON projects.id = enabled_modules.project_id AND enabled_modules.name IN ('forums') AND projects.active = True WHERE projects.active = True) ORDER BY journals.id DESC LIMIT 10
